{"tid":403473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用爐頭起爭執　玉蓮臺13歲兄刀傷10歲弟","createTime":"2017-09-17T08:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T23:23:11.000Z","uid":11050,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71b268b965209f8dea65e37931b00659a7ac7dda","tid":403473,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"牛頭角發生傷人案。下午1時許，玉蓮臺第3座1單位內，一對兄弟在廚房疑因爭用煮食爐發生拗撬，13歲兄長情緒激動拿起菜刀揮舞，誤傷10歲胞弟，弟弟右手及大腿受傷，父親見狀立即制止及報警。救護員到場為2兄弟治理後，一同送院，弟弟送院時狀甚輕鬆，擺出「V」字手勢，警方正調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170917/bkn-20170917140658141-0917_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170917%2Fbkn-20170917140658141-0917_00822_001.html&d=9ulIGd%2B19GD%2FoCX6EKh8F7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1e2ccc7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170917/bkn-20170917140658141-0917_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"57748dd87c1effaff72e2192b94470ebc0cc37d0","tid":403473,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e40b9e62af8aa723ca7fa9f8acb3c27ef2642d","tid":403473,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"爭煮嘢食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c839143b3cea63b3ae94bcebf918a8e32b83ef6","tid":403473,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:36:30.000Z","msg":"弟弟送院時狀甚輕鬆，擺出「V」字手勢"},{"pid":"078380379dc506ff6b76e65b2ada6e367b0b06ed","tid":403473,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"on 9"},{"pid":"88da28eeac97aed47a4fdd29b89d2349faf4481e","tid":403473,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"係咪真係v字呀"},{"pid":"ac97ae107679af1c8a1642ee59bada84666942bf","tid":40347